snippet.title: Crayon Physics Deluxe
snippet.description:
Me playing a game that I've been working on. 

I got a change to test the game on one of those notebook laptops. It's called Crayon Physics Deluxe and it's a sequel to a freeware game I did in June. The game's website is at http://www.kloonigames.com/crayon/

The music is _ghost - Lullaby and it's used under Creative Commons license.
